OL,7,FA man who sold his $79 million mansion
OL,8,Fto Jeff Bezos for less than asking
OL,9,Fprice is now suing his estate agent
OL,10,Fafter he allegedly failed to disclose
OL,11,Fthe Amazon CEO's identity.
OL,13,FThe seller alleges real-estate
OL,14,Fbrokerage, Douglas Elliman, which
OL,15,Fhandled both sides of the transaction,
OL,16,Fmisled him and at one point denied
OL,17,FBezos was the buyer.
