OL,7,FBezos secured a $6 million discount
OL,8,F(#4.6 million) on the seven-bedroom
OL,9,Fproperty, after negotiating the price
OL,10,Fwhile concealing his identity.
OL,12,FThe seller, toy company co-founder Leo
OL,13,FKryss, listed the waterfront company -
OL,14,Fwhich boasts a wine cellar, library
OL,15,Fand theatre - for $85 million in May
OL,16,F2023.
OL,18,FThe mansion is set on a private island
OL,19,Fnear Miami, dubbed the "Billionaire
OL,20,FBunker" - which also counts Tom Brady
OL,21,Fand Ivanka Trump among its residents.
