OL,7,FWhen an offer came in for his home
OL,8,Fshortly after Bezos paid $68 million
OL,9,Ffor the property next door, Kryss
OL,10,Fsuspected he was behind the bid for
OL,11,Fhis home, the Wall Street Journal
OL,12,Freports.
OL,14,FIt is alleged one of the brokerages'
OL,15,Femployees assured Kryss over the phone
OL,16,Fthat Bezos was not the buyer, and said
OL,17,Fthey would not pay more than $79
OL,18,Fmillion for the property.
