OL,7,FKryss agreed to the sale, but later
OL,8,Flearned that his house had indeed been
OL,9,Fsold to an entity linked to Bezos.
OL,11,FBezos, who also owns The Washington
OL,12,FPost, is worth an estimated $198
OL,13,Fbillion, or #151 billion.
OL,15,FKryss is now suing the brokerage for
OL,16,Fthe $6 million he believes he
OL,17,Fforfeited by not realising Bezos was
OL,18,Fthe buyer.
