OL,7,FIn the complaint, Kryss's lawyers say
OL,8,Fhe believed "it was highly material to
OL,9,Fhis negotiations and his decision on
OL,10,Fthe ultimate sales price of the Home
OL,11,Fto know whether Bezos was interested"
OL,12,Fand whether he was "attempting to
OL,13,Fanonymously acquire the home in order
OL,14,Fto assemble it with the adjoining
OL,15,Fproperty".
OL,17,FHis lawyer said in a statement:
OL,18,F"Douglas Elliman failed to fulfill
OL,19,Ftheir duties to our client."
