OL,7,F"They knew or should have known who
OL,8,Fthe ultimate beneficial purchaser was
OL,9,Fand misrepresented that very important
OL,10,Ffact to our client."
OL,12,FDouglas Elliman declined to comment.
OL,14,FIt is not uncommon for wealthy
OL,15,Findividuals to shield their identities
OL,16,Fthroughout the process of purchasing a
OL,17,Fhome, Miami real-estate agent Danny
OL,18,FHertzberg told The Wall Street Journal.
